    {
      "title": "<span id=\"#14084\" class=\"scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold flex items-center\"><h1 class=\"inline !mb-1 scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold\">expense</h1><div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(n.)</div></span>",
      "html": "<p>此外，前称为 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">expence</span> 的“花费或捐赠的行为，支出或开支，提供的经费，用作开支的款项，任何原因导致的损失或损害”，源自于14世纪晚期的盎格鲁-法语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">expense</span>，古法语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">espense</span> “提供开支的钱”，源自于 Late Latin <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">expensa</span> “经费，开支，支出”，是拉丁语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">expendere</span> “斟出货币，付款”的中性复数过去分词名词化，由 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">ex</span> “出，离开”（参见 <a href=\"/cn/word/ex-\" title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of ex- \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\">ex-</a>）和 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">pendere</span> “悬挂，使悬挂； 称量； 付款”（来自 PIE root <a href=\"/cn/word/*%28s%29pen-\" title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of *(s)pen- \" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"crossreference notranslate\">*(s)pen-</a> “拔，伸，旋转”）组成。关于拉丁动词的财务意义，参见 <a href=\"/cn/word/pound\" title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of pound \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\">pound</a>（n.1）。&nbsp; </p><ins class=\"adsbygoogle relative inline-block transition-all inline-block h-[250px] w-[300px]\" data-ad-slot=\"4000736339\" data-adtest=\"off\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"></ins><p>拉丁语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">spensa</i> 也产生了中世纪拉丁语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">spe(n)sa</i>，其意义专门指“食品开支”，后来指“食品”，然后被借用到古高地德语中作为 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">spisa</i> 的词根，并成为德语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">Speise</i> “食物”的词根，现在主要指“熟食”，以及 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">speisen</i> “吃”。<i class=\"foreign notranslate\"><strong>Expense account</strong></i> 来自1872年。</p>"
    },
    {
      "title": "<h2 id=\"#46809\" class=\"scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold flex items-center\">expense<div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(v.)</div></h2>",
      "html": "<p>\"把支出抵消掉收入\"，1909年，来自 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of expense \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/expense\">expense</a>（n.）。相关词汇： <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">Expensed</i>； <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">expensing</i>。</p>"
    }
  ],
